post_text:
In light of current events and school cancelations for the next three weeks, directing staff and school administration have made the decision to postpone the Spring Musical. We are continuing to encourage our kids to keep their hard work fresh through individual practice.

We are keeping an eye on the evolution of circumstances and will keep you updated on a possible rescheduling.

We do not want to make a call to cancel too quickly, but we are moving forward with all decisions with the best interest of the students and their health in mind. Check in for updates.

If you have any questions, please feel free to message us! Thank you for your patience and understanding!

-Mandie Heil
Director

post_text:
To everyone who came out last night... THANK YOU! We had an amazing opening night!

Also, because of this being the first year with a massive response to reserved seating, we wanted to thank you for your patience last night. We are making adjustments to speed up the ticket process and are addressing problems that cropped up last night to try to ensure they do not happen again!

Thank you again for all your support! Invite your friends and family and let our cast blow them away!
